Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\blur1\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:15.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:23.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:30.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:40.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:48.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:54.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:59.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:11.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:15.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:19.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:23.92,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(498.495,236.833)}The Creepy Bee Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.78,0:01:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachiko! Dinnertime!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...\NI'll just have to buy new ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:57.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\bord7\\3c&HD5DBBB&\c&HE3A792&}Kagemura Glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Try these.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe they'll\Nmeet your standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Sachiko?\NDo they suit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! They look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We've only just opened, but we're\Nalready getting wonderful reviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat it! It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw some that way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker requires your aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come to Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa? What's wrong, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa's acting weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there! Please get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be mean to my papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The glasses are calling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What was wrong with that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...\Nwas that really your papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She died... last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a pretty doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You pull the string\Nand it talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it's\Nbeen three days,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and still no sign\Nof Sachiko's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be one of\Nthose disappearances?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty-two people have gone\Nmissing over the past two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what could\Nbe causing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Did you learn something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who disappeared\Nhad just bought new glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And they all bought those glasses\Nfrom a boutique called Kagemura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll investigate the boutique.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shocker could be involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let you visit\Nsuch a dangerous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But the people didn't go missing\Ninside the shop, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true enough, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to buy\Nsome sunglasses anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Takeshi. Let me do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could go with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's an\Nexperiment I need to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:25.76,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,The lowest tone mammals\Ncan hear is 16 to 20 hertz.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:28.82,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,The highest is\Naround 25,000 hertz.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.84,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,But dogs can hear\Nsounds at 35,000 hertz.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But that day,\Nwith my modified hearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the sound of a\Nvibration inaudible to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was it coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The glasses are calling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the sound coming\Nfrom the glasses, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got back from\Nthe glasses shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The clerk was a little creepy,\Nbut nothing else seemed odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought some really cool ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to run a few more\Nexperiments, then come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't put those sunglasses\Non, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker is calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to us at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi... save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:10.06,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- The glasses won't come off!\N{\i1}- Hello? Hello?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.63,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Hello? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.73,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.25,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ruriko? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:09:04.09,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs50\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&}Midorikawa Ruriko
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The glasses must contain\Na special sensory device
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that can receive signals and\Nimages on a certain frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They use that to control\Npeople and make them disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:42.21,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Only Shocker would do something\Nso evil on such a broad scale...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:47.93,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\3c&H8EC2C9&\c&H000000&}Kagemura Glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, face me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,These nine are on\Ndisposal duty this week!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of all the people who have\Ngone missing to join Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you all have proved\Nexceptionally weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your inability to endure further\Nlabor at our gas production facility
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,has made you disposable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Please! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The best of you are altered and turned\Ninto Shocker combatants, like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Execute them all as part\Nof the gas testing process!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the gas valves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're part of this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you\Nto track us back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't interfere\Nnow, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing\Nsomething so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We need poison gas to\Ntake over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're a factory foreman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Receive an injection from\Nthis poisoned needle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do,\Nwe'll spare the woman's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're not just\Ngoing to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to paralyze you,\Nthen give you a complete cyborg surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... inject me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just release her, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:56.84,Bumper Episode 2-13,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(355,520)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, show me the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everyone, run away! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you move? Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to get out! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The stairway at the end\Nof the hall to your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are Ruriko or\NSachiko's father here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're all right.\NNow, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:59.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When wind spins the turbine in\Ncyborg Hongo Takeshi's belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:01.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he transforms into\Nthe Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi is still in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not in there any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:54.23,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I don't want Ruriko to know\Nabout my cyborg modifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.17,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Not until I can\Nreturn to normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Sachiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your papa's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,His memory has been erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way to cure it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... he should return\Nto normal soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But he probably won't remember\Nthe gas factory when he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an awful thing\Nto do to someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, are you still mad\NI broke your glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You are responsible\Nfor this failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... speak to\NShocker's boss on my behalf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker has no room for failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee Woman will avenge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So quiet down and\Ntake your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:17:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The great fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I let the girl escape\Nbecause I had a plan for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt Shocker will\Njust let this go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no knowing\Nwhat they'll try next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I made it as\Ndelicious as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you, Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done, Ruriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They were controlling her with\Nthose special sound waves again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I happened to hear the\Nsound, and it tipped me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So they stuck this on Ruriko\Nand returned her to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cruel thing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can trace this sound back to Bee\NWoman without having to follow her orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, look after Ruriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.22,0:22:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,People like you, who steal freedom\Nand disrupt peace, must pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What absolute tripe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.47,0:22:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.36,0:22:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't thank you enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.45,0:23:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.66,0:23:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.69,0:23:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa's feeling much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.74,0:23:27.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In some of the cars on this highway...\NIn fact, in places all over the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:31.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's minions lurk, plotting to\Nalter people to serve their own goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:35.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And every one of\Nthem must be stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:41.26,Cont,,560,0,145,,{\blur.8\fad(0,450)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:44.30,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(505.031,486.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:46.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.79,0:23:48.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Cobra Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:52.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Cobra Man's gang attacks the Ministry\Nof Finance's gold repository,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:55.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and Kamen Rider pursues him\Nto his base in the deep grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.79,0:23:58.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.71,0:24:01.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Monstrous Cobra Man!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:11.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.30,0:24:14.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.30,0:24:16.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.26,0:24:19.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:21.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.69,0:24:23.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.56,0:24:25.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.36,0:24:26.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.15,0:24:29.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.24,0:24:34.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.91,0:24:38.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.50,0:24:42.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.58,0:24:46.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!